---
layout: base.njk
title: Contact
description: Get in touch with HR Measured to discuss your analytics and measurement needs.
---

<section class="page-hero">
  <div class="container container--narrow">
    <div class="section-label">Contact</div>
    <h1>Let's talk.</h1>
    <p class="page-intro">I take on a small number of engagements at a time. If you're working on something where rigorous measurement or prediction would help, I'd like to hear about it.</p>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="contact-body">
  <div class="container container--narrow">
    <div class="contact-grid">
      <div class="contact-form-wrap">
        <form
          name="contact"
          method="POST"
          data-netlify="true"
          netlify-honeypot="bot-field"
          action="/thanks/"
        >
          <input type="hidden" name="form-name" value="contact" />
          <p class="hidden"><label>Don't fill this out: <input name="bot-field" /></label></p>

          <div class="form-group">
            <label for="name">Name</label>
            <input type="text" id="name" name="name" required autocomplete="name" />
          </div>

          <div class="form-group">
            <label for="email">Email</label>
            <input type="email" id="email" name="email" required autocomplete="email" />
          </div>

          <div class="form-group">
            <label for="organization">Organization</label>
            <input type="text" id="organization" name="organization" autocomplete="organization" />
          </div>

          <div class="form-group">
            <label for="message">What are you working on?</label>
            <textarea id="message" name="message" rows="6" required></textarea>
          </div>

          <button type="submit" class="btn btn--primary">Send Message</button>
        </form>
      </div>

      <div class="contact-info">
        <h3>What to expect</h3>
        <p>I respond to every inquiry personally, usually within two business days. If there's a potential fit, I'll suggest a 30-minute call to learn more about your situation.</p>
        <p>I'm not the right fit for every project — if I'm not, I'll tell you that and try to point you somewhere useful.</p>
        <div class="contact-direct">
          <p>Or reach me directly:</p>
          <a href="mailto:davidcmorris@hey.com" class="contact-email">davidcmorris@hey.com</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
